aqd:AQD_ReportingHeader.aqd:changeDescription: Retrospective delivery for UK 2013 environmental objectives Attainment statement (Df-G), includes bug fix for ozone ratification for Port Talbot Margam (UKA00501) and some syntax changes for declaration of adjustments. No additional exceedances observed relative to http://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/gb/eu/aqd/g/envvcusog/
